    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Press the saut\u00e9 button on the Instant Pot, add the oil and allow it to heat up for a minute. Add the cumin seeds and once they start to brown, add the onion and bay leaf. Stir-fry for 6-7 minutes or until the onion begins to brown."
    },
    {
